		{
			"name": "reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0T0xVSXlNVTlZZVRsdU1YVlpkeTFDWVZReGRHYxAB",
			"relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 месяцев назад",
			"rating": 2,
			"text": {
				"text": "I recently visited this clinic for a blood test. While the clinic itself is clean and the staff are friendly, I was very disappointed with the way the procedure was carried out.\nThe doctor put on gloves, then used the same gloves to type my information into the computer before proceeding to take my blood, which raises serious concerns about hygiene. The actual blood draw was also done poorly. It was more painful than any other experience I’ve had, and now I’m left with a swollen and bruised arm.\n\nI expected a more professional and careful approach from a medical facility. Unfortunately, this experience left me quite dissatisfied.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
			"originalText": {
				"text": "I recently visited this clinic for a blood test. While the clinic itself is clean and the staff are friendly, I was very disappointed with the way the procedure was carried out.\nThe doctor put on gloves, then used the same gloves to type my information into the computer before proceeding to take my blood, which raises serious concerns about hygiene. The actual blood draw was also done poorly. It was more painful than any other experience I’ve had, and now I’m left with a swollen and bruised arm.\n\nI expected a more professional and careful approach from a medical facility. Unfortunately, this experience left me quite dissatisfied.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
