			"relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 месяцев назад",
			"rating": 5,
			"text": {
				"text": "While on holiday in Tivat, my mum suffered a sudden back injury, and we were incredibly fortunate to find Milmedika. From the beginning, the staff were kind, attentive and truly went above and beyond to ensure she received care.\n\nEvery member of the team was professional yet warm and acted quickly to try and ease her pain. Unfortunately, the only option was to get her to a hospital in Podgorica and then a medevac flight home for spinal surgery.\n\nWe are so grateful for the outstanding service we received and can’t thank the team enough for their support during a difficult moment away from home. Highly recommended.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
			"originalText": {
				"text": "While on holiday in Tivat, my mum suffered a sudden back injury, and we were incredibly fortunate to find Milmedika. From the beginning, the staff were kind, attentive and truly went above and beyond to ensure she received care.\n\nEvery member of the team was professional yet warm and acted quickly to try and ease her pain. Unfortunately, the only option was to get her to a hospital in Podgorica and then a medevac flight home for spinal surgery.\n\nWe are so grateful for the outstanding service we received and can’t thank the team enough for their support during a difficult moment away from home. Highly recommended.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
